772
00:49:42,000 --> 00:49:43,740
You haven't escaped the whirlpool.

773
00:49:43,900 --> 00:49:47,780
You've just convinced yourself that stirring it faster is a form of control.

774
00:49:47,780 --> 00:49:51,480
As soon as you stop yelling, the walls of the valley are still there,

775
00:49:51,600 --> 00:49:52,980
and they are steeper than before.

776
00:49:53,640 --> 00:49:54,160
Okay.

777
00:49:55,060 --> 00:49:58,360
You have thoroughly destroyed my coping mechanisms.

778
00:49:59,040 --> 00:50:02,040
